5.2 Diversity, Equity & Inclusion

Targets Equity is one field of action in our DEGREE sustainability

framework that contributes to a greater sense of belonging for all our people. DEGREE ambition #9 – “30% female share in top management” – is aimed at continuously improving gender equity.1